Sentencas: In this paper, we develop two computational models,for the electrical performance of the tubular solid oxide fuel cell designed by Siemens Westinghouse Corporation.
Titulo: Modeling the performance of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The first model makes simplifying assumptions for activation and concentration polarizations and obtains an analytical solution.
Titulo: Modeling the performance of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In the second procedure, we allow the polarizations to vary with the current density and solve the equations numerically.
Titulo: Modeling the performance of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The results of the two methods are in good agreement with the experimentally quoted performance results.
Titulo: Modeling the performance of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Thus, the relatively simple analytical procedure can be used to predict the performance of the cell as a function of cell dimensions.
Titulo: Modeling the performance of a tubular solid oxide fuel cell
